      <title>德国财长肖尔茨认为欧盟在进一步扩大之前需要进行改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/germany-s-scholz-sees-need-for-eu-reform-before-more-enlargement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理表示，欧盟领导人需要就一系列改革达成一致，然后才能推进东扩，这可能会将几个西巴尔干国家以及乌克兰拉入欧盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/germany-s-scholz-sees-need-for-eu-reform-before-more-enlargement</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 15:44:30 GMT</pubDate>
