    <item>
      <title>几内亚将因能源枯竭而加深停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/guinea-to-deepen-power-cuts-with-energy-sources-depleted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几内亚国有电力公司表示，随着能源枯竭，将开始加深停电，并补充说其储备已不再充足。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/guinea-to-deepen-power-cuts-with-energy-sources-depleted</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 14:17:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
