      <title>墨西哥驻基多大使馆遭到袭击，与厄瓜多尔断绝关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/amlo-says-former-ecuador-vp-glas-taken-from-embassy-in-quito</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在警察冲进墨西哥驻基多大使馆后，墨西哥终止了与厄瓜多尔的外交关系，厄瓜多尔前副总统豪尔赫·格拉斯一直在那里庇护并拘留了他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/amlo-says-former-ecuador-vp-glas-taken-from-embassy-in-quito</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 04:49:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员梅嫩德斯及其妻子希望奢侈的生活方式在审判中被禁止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/senator-menendez-s-wife-wants-luxury-lifestyle-excluded-at-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员罗伯特·梅嫩德斯和他的妻子不希望陪审员在即将到来的腐败审判中了解这对权力夫妇的奢华生活方式，包括雪茄、手袋和珠宝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/senator-menendez-s-wife-wants-luxury-lifestyle-excluded-at-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 02:47:01 GMT</pubDate>
